{"tid":2201404,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中共威逼利誘推漢語　家長偕兒女匿草原　 內蒙校長護學生　辭職自殺","createTime":"2020-09-13T18:53:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-16T01:46:46.000Z","uid":240362,"like":140,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":72,"replies":[{"pid":"35769eb2bf35d2b3de8fe6a0ebf86d865327c4e3","tid":2201404,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T18:53:05.000Z","msg":"中共近月在內蒙古強推漢語教學，激起蒙人激烈反抗，蒙族人官員幹部亦加入抵制，蒙族家長甚至不讓孩子返校。中共軟硬兼施，派錢利誘學校及學生叫人回校，並以取消學籍作威脅；有家長帶學生到荒涼草原躲避。有指公安部長趙克志月初到內蒙古時曾下令鎮壓，但仍未能平息事件。昨日，內地消息又傳出，內蒙一名中學校長不願取消罷課學生學籍，辭職後自殺身亡，使蒙族人倍添憤怒。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200914/S74YXXNM75FSNKHUCV7UP5FERU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200914%2FS74YXXNM75FSNKHUCV7UP5FERU%2F&d=L%2FLAiDqbkajbTQHtoaAw8AwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=070e1fce\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200914%2FS74YXXNM75FSNKHUCV7UP5FERU%2F&h=e0ffebd1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200914/S74YXXNM75FSNKHUCV7UP5FERU/</a>"},{"pid":"38f7036baa77d89990528d0eb885db05c21f8342","tid":2201404,"uid":57374,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T18:57:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdb0186edecabc50921d1093f5551c1b56499a91","tid":2201404,"uid":253016,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T18:58:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支那"},{"pid":"6edec44f1ae2c8bb99977737efe33714260fad1f","tid":2201404,"uid":53026,"like":30,"dislike":17,"score":13,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T19:03:40.000Z","msg":"司徒老X大中華膠要鞭屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asse